1. Primary (Blue → #3B82F6 / blue-500)

Buttons (Add, Edit)

Links (<Link>)

Highlights on charts (main line/bar color)

Table headers background (blue-50)

Input focus rings

2. Secondary (Green → #34D399 / emerald-400)

Status badges (Active, Verified)

Secondary chart lines (growth rate, pass % etc.)

Positive metrics (+15%)

Secondary buttons (View)

3. Neutral (Gray Scale: gray-50 → gray-700)

Sidebar background → gray-50 or white

Page background → gray-50

Card background → white

Border separators → gray-200

Titles → gray-700

Body text → gray-500

4. Danger (Rose → #F43F5E / rose-500)

Delete actions

Error messages / validation

Negative chart values (expenses, dropout rates)

Alert badges